              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44935009/" class="">为什么你不该在人才市场找工作</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cp4/" class=" " title="cp4">cp4</a>
                (使世界更复杂一点点)
              
